[SN]TITLE[SN]
BBC presenter Colin Bloomfield backs skin cancer appeal

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A fund-raising appeal to help educate children in Derbyshire and East Staffordshire about how to stay safe in the sun has been started by the BBC and the Derby Telegraph.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
16 February 2015 Last updated at 20:47 GMT
It is backed by BBC presenter Colin Bloomfield who was diagnosed with melanoma and is still battling the disease.
